ipts. Prosecutors argue the former president was seeking to abuse the discovery process.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Tue, 08 Aug 2023 01:59:42 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/trump-evidence-witness-transcripts-january-6" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/desantis-trump-lost-2020-election" target="_blank">DeSantis says Trump ‘of course lost’ in 2020 when pressed in interview</a></h2><div class="description"> Florida Republican governor admits Biden won as Trump leads DeSantis by more than 30 points in most polling averages. The Florida governor and nearest challenger to Trump for the nomination in 2024 was asked: “Yes or no – did Donald Trump lose the 2020 election?”</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 07 Aug 2023 17:48:41 GMT</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">world</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">The Guardian</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/desantis-trump-lost-2020-election" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/aug/07/nancy-pelosi-indictments-against-trump-beautiful-intricate" target="_blank">Nancy Pelosi calls indictments against Trump ‘beautiful and intricate’</a></h2><div class="description"> Former House speaker Nancy Pelosi says indictments against Donald Trump are 'exquisite' and 'beautiful and intricate' Pelosi, 83, is a regular antagonist of the 77-year-old fo