 was no wonder Pietersen sent the bowlers on a leather hunt for the bowler. The former England batsman is one of cricket's most destructive cricketers.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Wed, 08 Apr 2020 10:31:29 +0530</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">entertainment</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">One India</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.oneindia.com/sports/cricket/kohli-was-destined-for-greatness-says-pietersen-3063154.html" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.oneindia.com/sports/football/bundesliga-game-week-7-roundup-results-2235794.html" target="_blank">Bundesliga game week 7: Roundup and results</a></h2><div class="description"> Ten-men Frankfurt held to a 2-2 draw against Bayern Munich. Cologne defeated Ingolstadt 2-1 to move at the second spot in the seventh round matches of the German Bundesliga. The German giants were unable to defend their two-goal lead in the Bundesliga.</div><br><span class="date"><strong>Published on:</strong> Mon, 17 Oct 2016 14:27:44 +0530</span><br><div class="category"><strong>Category: </strong><span class="category-text">sports</span></div><br><div class="source"><strong>Source: </strong><span class="source-text">One India</span></div><br><div class="link"><a href="https://www.oneindia.com/sports/football/bundesliga-game-week-7-roundup-results-2235794.html" target="_blank">Click here to read the full article</a></div><br></div><hr><div class='item'><h2><a href="https://www.oneindia.com/sports/cricket/rohit-sharma-plays-first-odi-at-wankhede-stadium-1909106.html" target="_blank">Rohit makes me laugh without even trying, says fiancee Ritika Sajdeh</a></h2><div class="description"> Rohit Sharma made his ODI debut in the year 2007 but it took him almost 8 years to play his first limited overs match in